  "description": "<p><strong>🔥Full-Time F&B Captain @ Tanjong Pagar 🔥</strong></p><p><strong></strong><br />💰 Salary: $3,200 – $3,500/month</p><p>🗓 Work Schedule: 5 days a week, 44 hours<br /></p><p><strong>Perks & Benefits:</strong></p><p>- Quarterly sales incentives program 💸</p><p>- Annual leave: From 10 days 🌴</p><p>- Loyalty bonus for long-term commitment 🏆<br /></p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><p>✅Lead and manage the team on daily operations to ensure smooth workflow.</p><p>✅Drive sales performance and achieve targets, motivating the team with incentives.</p><p>✅Provide excellent customer service, handling customer inquiries and feedback.</p><p><strong>✅</strong>Maintain inventory, stock levels, and store cleanliness.</p><p>✅Train and mentor team members to ensure consistent service standards.</p><p>✅Monitor and enforce compliance with company policies and safety standards.</p><p>✅Report daily performance, sales, and team updates to management.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>✨Relevant experience in a supervisory or captain role (F&B or retail experience preferred)</p><p>✨Strong leadership and team management skills </p><p>✨Excellent customer service and communication skills</p><p>✨Sales-driven mindset with ability to motivate and coach the team</p><p>✨Ability to handle daily operations, inventory, and reporting</p><p>✨Reliable, proactive, and committed to achieving team goals<br /></p><p>Join a dynamic team, grow your career, and enjoy great incentives!<br /></p><p>📩 WHATSAPP wa.me/6589387313 TO APPLY🎊<br /></p><p>Code: <strong>CAPTAIN</strong></p><p>Full name:</p><p>Residential area:</p><p>Earliest availability date:</p><p>Commitment period:</p><p>Able to work on weekends?:</p><p>And please attached a copy of your resume</p><p>https://t.me/sgbesttempjobs</p><p>https://t.me/varioustempjobs<br /></p><p>Chia Xin Ee Crystal | R21103390</p><p>EA License No: 21C0626</p>",
